== Bhov Mogall Mai - Gaion ==

Bhov mogall Mai
Most Loving Mother
Type: Hymn
Source: Gaionacho Jhelo, 1995 edition, T-12
Lyrics: Traditional
Music: Traditional. Chords: Bernardo Cota, Santa Cruz, Ilhas, [[गोंय|Goa]]
Publisher: Goychi Sevadhormik Somoti (Pastoral Institute), Old [[गोंय|Goa]], [[गोंय|Goa]] 403 402
Translated by: Alfred Noronha, Pandavaddo, Chorão, [[गोंय|Goa]] 403 102. August 2005

Refrain:

Maiê kakutichê, Maiê mogachê,

Merciful Mother, loving Mother,

Maiê sorv xegunnamnim bhôrlelê.

Mother,rich in virtues.



Bhov mogall Mai (Maiê)

Very loving Mother

amche thãi tum rav,

stay with us,

gorzank akantak

sodanch tum pav.

be always our help in our needs and fears.


Amcheam gorzamnim,

In our times of need,

amcheam dukhamnim,

in our sorrows,

amcheam vignamnim,

in our tribulations,

pav tum sodim.

come to our aid,


Amchê khatir

On our behalf

Puta lagim mag,

plead to Your Son,

favo kôr amkam

to make us worthy

sorginchem bhag.

of heavenly bliss.


